profile:
H & I Roofing Ltd, based out of Maple Ridge, British Columbia. We have over three decades of experience with the installation of a wide variety of roofing materials. We provide service throughout the Lower Mainland and the Fraser Valley in both new construction as well as reroofs. H & I has completed projects throughout BC & into Alberta ranging from residential stratas to large commercial projects. With our hardworking, ethical, and efficient crew, no project is too big or too small! H & I Roofing owns and operates all of itâ€™s own equipment and vehicles. From the crane truck that delivers the roofing materials directly to your roof, to the disposal trailers that are towed off of your property as soon as they full. Our customers are always impressed by the excellent service that H & I is able to provide at such competitive rates. Most of the re-roofs and new roofs are finished within a day. 

Winner of Portrait Homes 2011 Safety Award
services: New Roof, Re-Roof, Metal Roofing, Torch on and Roof Inspection
specialities:
Sloped and Flat Roof assemblies and Installation
Re roof - Residential and Strata
